un m'hot UNK dos, di daytshn hobn undz farkhapt.

00:04:57.197 --> 00:04:59.452
UNK tsu forn keyner.

00:05:00.690 --> 00:05:04.970
un m'hot ⟨zikh di⟩, hot zikh ongehoybn in ende YUL'

00:05:05.415 --> 00:05:07.299
in eyn un fertsikstn yor

00:05:07.423 --> 00:05:10.404
geven mitvokh, zenen arayn tsu undz di daytshn.

00:05:12.385 --> 00:05:19.044
tsvey teg hobn zey n- keynem nisht getshepet. s'iz gegan der f- de- der front. der krig iz geven

00:05:19.692 --> 00:05:25.406
un ersht frayt- fraytik zenen arayn in ey- nokh tsugekumen di rumener

00:05:25.750 --> 00:05:29.321
un shabes hobn zey shoyn geharget a yidn vos er hot gedavnt.

00:05:30.171 --> 00:05:32.732
un zuntik hot men shoyn ongehoybn traybn

00:05:32.732 --> 00:05:33.776
ale yidn.

00:05:33.833 --> 00:05:36.409
s'ershte hobn zey genumen di mener

00:05:36.870 --> 00:05:40.273
un dernokh hobn zey ongehoybn traybn di kinder mit di froyen.

00:05:41.781 --> 00:05:44.798
mayn foter hot men genumen friert mit ale mener

00:05:44.798 --> 00:05:49.672
un ven m'hot undz shoyn gefirt un m'hot undz arayngevorfn in a keler, s'hot men geharget

00:05:49.813 --> 00:05:51.827
iz shoyn geven a sakh gehargete

00:05:51.827 --> 00:05:55.210
un der foter hot undz derzen, hot er ongehoybn shrayen, zenen mir

00:05:55.210 --> 00:05:59.214
tsuge- -lofn, ⟨ven er⟩ iz geven in der zayt ⟨vu er⟩

00:05:59.398 --> 00:06:02.362
un s'iz geven shtark a sakh ongehargete mentshn

00:06:02.520 --> 00:06:06.390
hot, dos iz geven, fun di vent hot zikh gegosn

00:06:06.390 --> 00:06:11.627
vaser mit, mit blut. azoy fil geven. s'iz geven ende YUL'. s'iz geven shtark heys

00:06:12.257 --> 00:06:19.811
hot der foter zikh oysgerisn fun undz, un er zogt er vil zikh avekleygn f- fornt, me zol im hargenen, vayl UNK m'vet fun danet nisht aroys.

00:06:20.256 --> 00:06:22.325
un ikh bin geblibn mit der muter

00:06:22.467 --> 00:06:24.064
un zi hot mikh ongehoybn

00:06:24.323 --> 00:06:25.397
f- bahaltn

00:06:25.555 --> 00:06:30.729
az se zol blaybn fun ir a zeykher, az ikh zol nisht derharget vern. zi hot mikh farshtelt.

00:06:30.988 --> 00:06:36.112
nor far dem vos zi hot m- zi iz geharget gevorn, iz, m'hot zi geshosn

00:06:36.355 --> 00:06:39.386
hot zi nokh mir gezogt eyn vort, "gey"

00:06:40.118 --> 00:06:42.738
un ikh hob nisht farshtanen vos

00:06:42.738 --> 00:06:46.738
un ikh bin gegan. ikh bin aroysgekrokhn. ikh bin aroysgekrokhn, iz shoyn geven farnakht.

00:06:47.138 --> 00:06:48.906
es hot gegosn a regn

00:06:48.906 --> 00:06:50.490
un m'hot shoyn nisht gehakt

00:06:51.255 --> 00:06:58.572
un azoy vi ikh bin gelign in, lebn keler vu m'hot geharget, iz aroysgekrokhn a yingele, f- undzers a shokhn

00:06:59.018 --> 00:07:04.091
un di mo- muter mitn foter mit a shvesterl mit a bruderl zenen derharget gevorn

00:07:04.215 --> 00:07:07.685
un er azoy gelign lebn mir in der vaser vos hot geregnt

00:07:08.164 --> 00:07:12.793
un er hot shtark geveynt. er iz geven klener fun mir. ikh bin geven alt nayn yor, un er iz geven alt zibn

00:07:12.793 --> 00:07:17.692
iz er arayngekrokhn tsurik in keler, un er hot ongehoybn shrayen tsu der muter

00:07:17.698 --> 00:07:20.234
un mayn foter iz gelign fornt

00:07:20.234 --> 00:07:24.813
hot er derkent dem kol fun dem yingele, vayl er iz geven a shokhn undzerer

00:07:24.837 --> 00:07:27.767
hot er im gezogt az ayer Manye ligt in droysn

00:07:28.110 --> 00:07:30.399
un der foter iz aroysgegangen

00:07:30.473 --> 00:07:32.914
fun dortn. s'iz shoyn geven fintster

00:07:33.325 --> 00:07:40.443
un hot mir gefregt "vu iz di mame?" hob ikh gezogt "di mame iz derharget gevorn." hot er mikh arayngenumen tsurik un hot oyfgehoybn di toyte

00:07:40.443 --> 00:07:43.919
un hot mikh arayngeleygt tsvishn di toyte un hot mir fardekt mit zey

00:07:43.919 --> 00:07:45.756
mistome vet mir nokh shisn

00:07:46.015 --> 00:07:48.321
zol ikh blaybn lebn.

00:07:48.546 --> 00:07:52.488
nor zey hobn shoyn meyn nisht geshosn. s'iz shoyn geven shtark fintster

00:07:53.895 --> 00:07:56.535
zenen mir opgelegn biz shpet bay nakht

00:07:56.535 --> 00:08:00.535
un bay nakht hot er hot er mir genumen oyf di hent, un mir zenen gan tsun undz in shtub.

00:08:00.595 --> 00:08:05.769
bay undz in shtub iz shoyn gornisht geven. aldings iz geven aroysgetrogn. di fentster zenen geven tseklapt

00:08:05.995 --> 00:08:09.769
nor mit undz durkh eyn koridor hot gevoynt a eltere froy

00:08:10.348 --> 00:08:15.776
zenen mir arayngan atin. mir hobn zikh arayngeleygt i- bay ir in bet, un mir hobn zikh fardekt mit kishns

00:08:15.934 --> 00:08:18.066
un gants fri hobn mir e- gehert redn

00:08:18.066 --> 00:08:19.202
vi me redt

00:08:19.630 --> 00:08:24.602
iz arayngegangen, nor dos iz geven goyim funem dorf vos zey hobn gerabevet

00:08:25.047 --> 00:08:28.439
hobn zey undz gegebn, aropgenumen bay undz di kishns

00:08:28.439 --> 00:08:31.959
un m'hot, hobn mir zikh oyfgezetst, zenen zey antlofn

00:08:31.959 --> 00:08:36.229
bin ikh ongehoybn mitn foter tsu loyfn. mir zenen arayn g- in dorf arayn

00:08:36.859 --> 00:08:39.840
hot undz bagegnt a k- a goye

00:08:39.998 --> 00:08:41.747
un hot undz gegebn a trunk

00:08:41.803 --> 00:08:48.800
vayl ikh bin geven ful dos ponem mitn, dos, dos moyl mit ⟨prishtshes⟩ vos m'hot geshosn a gantsn tog un keyn trinken iz nisht geven

00:08:49.144 --> 00:08:57.305
hot zi gezogt az dort iz do bay un- in d- in di gertner kent ir zikh bahaltn, vayl vu m'hot gepakt a yidn, hot men im nokh derharget

00:08:57.953 --> 00:09:00.782
hobn mir zikh avekgeleygt mitn foter dortn

00:09:00.923 --> 00:09:02.978
un ikh hob gevolt shtark a trunk

00:09:02.978 --> 00:09:05.888
zogt er mir "do voynt eyner vos er ken undz.

00:09:05.888 --> 00:09:10.318
gey tsu, bist a kind, vet men UNK azoy dikh nit zen, un er vet dir gebn a trunk

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:14.011
un ikh bin tsugan, hot er mir gegebn a trunk. ikh bin gegangen tsurik

00:09:14.136 --> 00:09:16.908
hob ikh geshribn "pape"

00:09:16.908 --> 00:09:19.783
un di goyim zogn oyf ukraynish "TATA"

00:09:19.840 --> 00:09:23.968
iz gelign a yidishe mishpokhe

00:09:24.008 --> 00:09:28.322
hobn zey farshtanen az s'iz a yidish kind, hobn zey mir genumen ts- tsu zikh.

00:09:28.345 --> 00:09:32.206
der foter iz opgelign a tsvey sho, un er hot gezen az ikh bin nishto

00:09:32.206 --> 00:09:33.648
iz er tsugekumen

00:09:33.648 --> 00:09:36.374
tsu dem krist un nokh gefregt ⟨vuhin⟩ ikh bin

00:09:36.374 --> 00:09:39.760
hot er gekhapt a hak un zogt "az du geyst nit avek, vel ikh dir bald tsehakn

00:09:39.760 --> 00:09:41.045
vayl du bist a yid."

00:09:41.642 --> 00:09:43.959
geyt er shoyn vayter un heybt on veynen

00:09:43.959 --> 00:09:47.795
iz aroyfgan a ander kristlekhe. zi zogt az do lign epes yidn

00:09:48.190 --> 00:09:50.361
hot ⟨dokh ⟩ der pape mikh gefunen

00:09:51.278 --> 00:09:54.018
un hot zi ongehoybn shrayen az me

00:09:54.018 --> 00:09:57.708
me UNK ir aldings vos se vakst dortn

00:09:57.708 --> 00:09:59.788
az mir zoln zikh geyn fun danet

00:09:59.867 --> 00:10:03.264
iz ikh mitn foter, zenen mir arayngan, s'iz do azoyne shtekhers

00:10:03.264 --> 00:10:05.141
hobn mir zikh arayngerukt atin

00:10:05.141 --> 00:10:06.131
un di froy

00:10:06.131 --> 00:10:08.861
mitn, mitn man mit a yingele

00:10:08.861 --> 00:10:10.331
zenen gelign vayter

00:10:10.331 --> 00:10:13.151
un in a sho arum hot men zey gepakt, un me hot zey gehakt

00:10:13.151 --> 00:10:17.006
un mir zenen opgelign dray teg on esn un on trinken

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:19.031
un s'hot ongehoybn tsu regenen

00:10:19.071 --> 00:10:22.511
iz dos hobn mir getrunken, zogt der foter "veyst vos? mir veln

00:10:22.511 --> 00:10:24.281
pavolye mit di gertner

00:10:24.281 --> 00:10:25.716
tsugeyn in shtot

00:10:25.716 --> 00:10:28.239
veln mir zen iz geblibn emetser lebn

00:10:28.239 --> 00:10:31.620
iz gut. anit ⟨vet men undz⟩ oykhet, vos zoln mir lign ot ot azoy o?"

00:10:31.710 --> 00:10:33.403
iz hobn mir zikh tsugerukt

00:10:33.403 --> 00:10:36.727
iz geshtanen a froy un hot genumen vaser. f- s'hot geregnt

00:10:36.727 --> 00:10:40.094
zogt zi "s'iz do in, do in yeshive etlekhe geranite

00:10:40.094 --> 00:10:42.049
di geranite hobn zey nisht geharget.

00:10:42.595 --> 00:10:48.377
zenen mir arayngan, un m'hot ongehoybn, ver s'iz geblibn hot ongehoybn shtark veynen, vayl bay yedn iz emetser g-

00:10:48.518 --> 00:10:49.457
gefaln.

00:10:51.488 --> 00:10:54.891
hobn zey undz gezogt az ir vet dos zayn, vet men aykh ⟨asoben⟩ hargenen

00:10:55.318 --> 00:10:57.607
un mir hobn gehat a heymishe kristlekhe

00:10:58.103 --> 00:11:00.527
⟨vos⟩ zi hot gezogt az mir zoln geyn tsun ir

00:11:05.325 --> 00:11:07.934
zenen mir gegangen tsun ir bay nakht

00:11:08.498 --> 00:11:11.372
hot zi undz arayngeleygt dortn vu di ku iz

00:11:11.372 --> 00:11:12.626
in der shtroy

00:11:13.476 --> 00:11:14.738
un hot gezogt

00:11:14.738 --> 00:11:16.974
"lig dortn bay undz a por teg"

00:11:16.974 --> 00:11:21.620
nor di daytshn hobn ongehoybn nemen shtroy, zogt zi "m'vet aykh pakn, vet men undz hargenen"

00:11:21.745 --> 00:11:26.768
un der front iz gan bay undz etle- etlekhe teg, vayl s'iz a veg fun finef vegn

00:11:28.157 --> 00:11:34.968
es iz gegangen, un der front hot zikh, zenen gegan vayter. di daytshn zenen avekgan, un s'iz geblibn keyner nit geblibn bay undz in shtot

00:11:35.599 --> 00:11:38.996
es iz gegan. hot ⟨er krik⟩ gekumen un zogt "keyner iz nishto

00:11:38.996 --> 00:11:42.022
s'iz geblibn ver, s'iz geblibn geranit, un ver se

00:11:42.028 --> 00:11:46.392
geyt aroys vos hot zikh gebahaltn ergets, un ver s'iz geblibn fun di kelers"

00:11:46.804 --> 00:11:48.435
hobn mir zikh umgekert

00:11:48.559 --> 00:11:51.911
tsurik in shtot. bay undz in shtub iz shoyn gornisht geven

00:11:52.862 --> 00:11:58.993
un azoy hobn mir zikh tsunoyfgenumen di etlekhe yidn, ver s'iz geblibn, ver s'iz geven geranit, un ver s'iz geven azoy

00:11:58.993 --> 00:12:02.306
un di mentshn zenen, di gehargete zenen gelign in di kelers

00:12:02.565 --> 00:12:05.039
iz bay undz geven eyner a feldsher

00:12:05.080 --> 00:12:06.441
⟨VOSKOBOYNIK⟩

